 109	///
 110	/// For positive rates this computes `-ln(U) / lambda`, where `U` is the open
 111	/// uniform sample for the same coordinates. Per `DESIGN.md` §4.3, non-positive
 112	/// rates return [`f64::INFINITY`], meaning that the transition never fires.
